summary:
ive never loved, respected or valued a person like I do with Keanu Reeves.
that man has been through some tough fucking shit...
body:
ive never loved, respected or valued a person like I do with Keanu Reeves.

that man has been through some tough fucking shit man, he’s a credit to those who he lost along the way, he’s a credit to himself for being here, being a kind soul…giving his money to strangers, helping those who need it you know!? and he doesn’t want any credit or award for his generosity or kindness.

im grateful to have someone like THAT to look up to.

i hope one day he finds love and continues to make beautiful movies for us to enjoy.


that’s all I gotta say.
